The paper focuses on query suggestion, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed model uses neural networks, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The attention mechanism used in the model is a popular technique in deep learning (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with user behavior and preferences, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
